             was indicted for <rs id="t18020428-92-off484" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18020428-92-off484" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18020428-92-off484" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18020428-92-cd485" type="crimeDate">1st of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020428-92-off484 t18020428-92-cd485"></join>, a cloak, value 18s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18020428-92-victim690" type="victimName">
                           Emanuel 
                           Moses
                        <interp inst="t18020428-92-victim690" type="surname" value="Moses"></interp>
